title: The O'Doyle's Do Rule  (feat. Shane Gillis)
description: DJ Lou’s date gets friendly with a comic at The Comedy Cellar. Big Jay explains why Bon Jovi is much better than Bruce Springsteen & Shane Gillis joins Dan and Jay in discussing who the real bullies are in some very famous movies.
author: podcasts@siriusxm.com (Comedy Central)
